Free Packages

This page is generated dynamically and lists most free packages that can be activated if you own base game, including demos.

109 packages that can not be activated in Singapore (as far as we know) were filtered. Click here to ignore filters.

If you want to hide demos, click here to hide demos and legacy media.

If you want to only view content for your owned games, click here to only show these.

How to use this?
  • Install our browser extension
  • Login into Steam store in this browser
  • Close Steam if you have it running to prevent lag
  • Click Activate these packages now button
  • Leave the page open, it will automatically run every hour
  • Only 50 packages can be activated per hour on Steam
  • Keep in mind that free games will not give +1 to your game count
Use our browser extension for this page to work.
Setting "Highlight owned and wished products on steamdb.info" must be enabled in the extension.
